                <head>[Memorandum.]</head>
                <p>Colonel Mazuera was informed by me verbally of the foregoing, and he replied that
                    he would have been glad to pay a visit of courtesy to the President and the
                    Secretary of State.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>R. S. CHEW, <hi rend="italic">Chief Clerk.</hi>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-05-26">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">May</hi> 26, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
